  "body": "#### System information\r\n\r\nErigon version: `./erigon --version`\r\n````\r\nerigon version 2022.07.1-alpha-09776394\r\n````\r\nErigon running options:\r\n````\r\n./erigon --chain=rinkeby  --port=30303  --private.api.addr=127.0.0.1:9090  --http --http.addr=0.0.0.0 --http.vhosts=* --http.port=8545 --http.api=eth,debug,net,trace,web3,erigon --ws --torrent.download.rate=20mb --torrent.port=42069 --prune=htrc\r\n````\r\n\r\nErigon on the rinkeby returns incorrect  gas price value\r\nActual gasPrice\r\n````\r\ncurl -X POST --header \"Content-Type: application/json\" --data '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"eth_gasPrice\",\"params\":[],\"id\":1}' http://localhost:8545\r\n{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":1,\"result\":\"0x11a\"}\r\n````\r\nBehavior gasPice (get from geth)\r\n````\r\ncurl -X POST --header \"Content-Type: application/json\" --data '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"eth_gasPrice\",\"params\":[],\"id\":1}' http://172.17.0.3:8545\r\n{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":1,\"result\":\"0x59682efe\"}\r\n````",
